    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8687259461961217569.png",
                "id": "talent69871",
                "key": "Strike of the Dispossessed",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Strike of the Dispossessed"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>, mengambil 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span>, dan menciptakan 1 lapis <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oasis Nourishment</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat memainkan Awaken, My Kindred:</span> mengonsumsi 1 Dadu Elemental lebih sedikit.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span> (Dapat ditumpuk hingga 3)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/b5c63ab0dca603b7744290cd57df7ba6_315629572998887258.png",
                "id": "talent68074",
                "key": "Life Stream",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Life Stream"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, mengambil 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span>, dan menciptakan 2 lapis <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oasis Nourishment</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat memainkan Awaken, My Kindred:</span> mengonsumsi 1 Dadu Elemental lebih sedikit.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span> (Dapat ditumpuk hingga 3)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/7abf617a4cbf7dfd0d8af8ea344109a0_574846903822119897.png",
                "id": "talent70778",
                "key": "The End Falls",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "The End Falls"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Menciptakan 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Awaken, My Kindred</span> saat duel dimulai dan diletakkan secara acak ke dalam Dek-mu. Setelah kamu memanggil 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Proliferated Organism</span>, Karakter ini mendapatkan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Reignited Heart of Oasis</span> dan memperoleh 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Perisai</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Reignited Heart of Oasis</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>Karakter yang terpengaruh mengakibatkan DMG +3.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah Karakter yang terpengaruh menggunakan Skill:</span> menghapus <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oasis Nourishment</span> di areamu dan setiap 1 lapis yang dihapus akan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter yang terpengaruh.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/78668ff054322fa748bbe935edb4a58e_3317323399288463471.png",
                "id": "talent93938",
                "key": "Invokation of Propagation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Invokation of Propagation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Kartu Peristiwa</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat memainkan kartu ini atau membuang kartu ini:</span> memanggil 1 Proliferated Organism terpisah.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3513161494796071688.png",
                "id": "talent54616",
                "key": "Awaken, My Kindred",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_2173975813908838374.png",
                "title": "Awaken, My Kindred"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>. </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3086133044603111856.png",
                "id": "talent92693",
                "key": "Proliferated Organism",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_2258324503152093480.png",
                "title": "Proliferated Organism"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Dendro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG ke kasus Pyro atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, membuat [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang akan mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan 1 kali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_864129052343376199.png",
                "id": "talent24302",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Buang</span></strong></p><p>Gunakan efek Kartu Aksi atau Skill Karakter untuk membuang Kartu Aksi dari Tangan atau Dek-mu.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Perisai</span></strong></p><p>Saat Karakter yang dilindungi Perisai menerima DMG, Perisai akan terkonsumsi untuk menahan DMG yang diterima.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3359091554148482772.png",
                "id": "talent86272",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
